casebody.data:
BOLIVARIAN REPUBLIC OF VENEZUELA, et al., applicant,
v.
HELMERICH & PAYNE INTERNATIONAL DRILLING CO., et al. No. 15A258. Supreme Court of the United States Sept. 1, 2015.

UPON CONSIDERATION of the application of counsel for the applicant,

IT IS ORDERED that the application for stay of mandate in the above-entitled case is denied.
